WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Create a Collection

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Go to "Variables" tab

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:14.000
Create a variable named "baseUrl" and put your API's URL

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:17.000
Add a request

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:22.000
Use the curly brace syntax to insert the variable in your request's URL
(e.g. {{baseUrl}}))

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:25.000
Click "Send"

